msgid "Caveats"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../docs/en/public-address/integrated-address.md:52
msgid "There are some caveats:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: ../docs/en/public-address/integrated-address.md:54
msgid "Single transaction cannot pay to multiple integrated addresses."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: ../docs/en/public-address/integrated-address.md:56
msgid ""
"As individual running a wallet you should generally prefer subaddresses. "
"However, if you happen to use integrated addresses, you should allow Monero "
"software to generate integrated addresses for you (instead of forcing your "
"own payment IDs)."
msgstr ""

